Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Masscan requires root privileges

Solution: Use sudo with masscan commands or configure capabilities
Issue: NSE scripts not found

Solution: Update NSE database with nmap --script-updatedb
Issue: Python scripts fail with import errors

Solution: Install required packages: pip3 install schedule
Issue: Scans timeout or hang

Solution: Reduce scan rate, use smaller port ranges, or increase timeout values
Issue: XML parsing errors

Solution: Verify XML files are complete and well-formed; check for scan errors
